{panel:bgColor=#fffae6}
*Developer Information* 

* It is due to the useSKUPricing hook implementation to rely on [subscription's delivery portion handle|https://github.com/hellofresh/web/blob/master/app/spaces/whitelabel/modules/whitelabel-web/packages/libraries/services/prices/hooks/useSkuPricing.ts#L11]  triggering redundant API call once the subscription is successfully updated as the delivery option of subscription gets changed.This means {{/calculate}} endpoint is used with wrong deliveryOption throughout the change plan flow but BE is still returning the correct price, but for whatever the reason, the BE is temporarily returning wrong price info when the payload is correct.
* Potential fix would be to update the implementation of useSKUPricing to always use the delivery option of the respective SKU (for the payload integrity) which would eventually prevent this additional API call creating the flickering
* Video: [https://hellofresh.slack.com/archives/G018LQBLWGZ/p1767859203567059|https://hellofresh.slack.com/archives/G018LQBLWGZ/p1767859203567059|smart-link] 
{panel}

